videos.description: Khris Middleton steps up with 40 points and Giannis adds 26 in the Bucks' 109-103 win over the Suns in Game 4.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Middleton, Giannis combine for 66 points as Bucks even the Finals) 2021// ESHEET SVP SC

videos.headline: Middleton, Giannis combine for 66 points as Bucks even the Finals

videos.description: After defeating the Suns in Game 4 to tie the series, Khris Middleton explains to Malika Andrews that the Bucks' main focus is to figure out how to play the same on the road as they do at home.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Middleton focused on how to maintain consistency on the road) 2021/07/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Middleton focused on how to maintain consistency on the road

videos.description: Chris Paul explains why he believes the Suns will step up their game after a tough Game 4 loss to the Bucks on the road.

videos.headline: CP3 vows Suns will play better in Game 5
